{"tid":2216050,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（又來料）李克強身陷「人海」 習近平獨站「大圈」","createTime":"2020-09-24T11:30:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-26T17:13:11.000Z","uid":184679,"like":207,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"f33bbab400324ab6b0429681ec42e3b990a8d6d3","tid":2216050,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T11:30:59.000Z","msg":"中共五中全會臨近，習近平和李克強開始頻繁露面，二人又擦出不少「火花」。網上傳出的視頻顯示，李克強日前到上海視察，現身人山人海的南京路，與民眾「親密接觸」。而習近平在湖南卻獨自一人站在10米大圈中，向民眾「喊」話，倍顯孤獨。<br />\n<br />\n李克強9月21日至22日到上海考察，他在人山人海的南京路逛步行街的一段視頻刷爆網路。網友在推特上發布的視頻顯示，21日晚，李克強戴著口罩和隨行人員逛南京路，還來到一個鋪位買了兩包大白兔奶糖。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img001.21cnimg.com/photos/album/20200923/o/2C0F07C5E95C314D039C8ADAA440D9D3.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg001.21cnimg.com%2Fphotos%2Falbum%2F20200923%2Fo%2F2C0F07C5E95C314D039C8ADAA440D9D3.jpeg&h=3c498d5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n該推友調侃說，「一把手都開抗疫表彰大會了，你還戴口罩，這是不給面子啊！」「給現金，不率先使用數字貨幣，差評！」<br />\n<br />\n另一段視頻顯示，李克強站在步行街上，周圍人山人海，李克強揮手和民眾互動。這和習近平在湖南郴州市考察時站在大圈裡，向圈外民眾「喊話」的場景，形成鮮明對比。<br />\n<br />\n據中共黨媒報導，習近平9月16日到湖南郴州市汝城縣文明瑤族鄉沙洲瑤族村考察，習獨自一人站在一個直徑10米的大圈中心，他的保鏢、隨行人員以及當地民眾全都站在圈外。<br />\n<br />\n習近平站在圈裡向圈外人「喊話」，黨媒卻聲稱，習近平在同村民和遊客們「親切交流」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ntdtv.com/assets/uploads/2020/09/7923395923f95a977fa2af25196e40e9-600x338.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ntdtv.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2F7923395923f95a977fa2af25196e40e9-600x338.jpg&h=c8c953d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n推特網友調侃說：「李克強現身上海南京路。人山人海。和習一出現到處戒嚴且和民眾保持一定距離有鮮明對比！不知習會不會開心呢？」<br />\n<br />\n「李克強盡往人多的地方跑。因為他在中央太孤獨了！」<br />\n<br />\n「行為上，中堂已經接近一個反賊了。」<br />\n<br />\n「感覺老李就是在混日子，等下課那一天&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2020/09/24/a102947916.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com%2Fb5%2F2020%2F09%2F24%2Fa102947916.html&d=6i5jd82mnfhmr%2B7rEyOheAmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=eb0452c8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2020/09/24/a102947916.html</a>"},{"pid":"c9cb577b93bcc7970e267a4f5cff270b5b2892c0","tid":2216050,"uid":20170,"like":218,"dislike":1,"score":217,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T11:34:46.000Z","msg":"有人與我爭奪人心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57602abdea671f5ba001f8a75a42d8e0cd475c7c","tid":2216050,"uid":291526,"like":148,"dislike":1,"score":147,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T11:35:01.000Z","msg":"強仔玩命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再係咁皇上隨時賜佢坐十年八年<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdc11e9ee2f5a8c25f45ff477ac31aacd70d850c","tid":2216050,"uid":155095,"like":180,"dislike":2,"score":178,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T11:35:59.000Z","msg":"劉少奇2.0 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://res.img.ifeng.com/2011/1121/xes_fdd71cdf615ea36f27ce3dcb72447bb2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fres.img.ifeng.com%2F2011%2F1121%2Fxes_fdd71cdf615ea36f27ce3dcb72447bb2.jpg&h=17686e1d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"da9e9bedfbf135f9c204ef1ba00e1703b3b2764f","tid":2216050,"uid":156375,"like":195,"dislike":4,"score":191,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T11:37:49.000Z","msg":"兩條友扮不和搞花邊嘢轉移視線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca145690abf66995cc1ea5c18f7c2cab3b669ef3","tid":2216050,"uid":244034,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T11:41:01.000Z","msg":"皇上點可以同D賤民企咁近架，呢啲一品冇所為啦"},{"pid":"4ac38073114e6fda488fb5f045a7a6fd10596f00","tid":2216050,"uid":7125,"like":76,"dislike":2,"score":74,"quote":{"pid":"da9e9bedfbf135f9c204ef1ba00e1703b3b2764f","tid":2216050,"uid":156375,"like":195,"dislike":4,"score":191,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T11:37:49.000Z","msg":"兩條友扮不和搞花邊嘢轉移視線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T11:44:28.000Z","msg":"上面真係有需要攪呢啲咩<img src=\"